               Title: Department Head and Group Leader
Craig A Huff's Experience
Title: Sales
               Company: CIP International Inc
Job Details
               CIP was founded in 1975 by Thomas and Kathleen Huff, and has become a world leader in supermarket design, retail design and décor fabrication. Over the years, CIP has built its reputation as a company which independent and chain retailers alike can turn to for innovative customized solutions that connect with their clientele. Today, CIP serves clients, both large and small, throughout the United States as well as Latin America, the Caribbean, Asia and the Middle East. A key ingredient of CIP's success is continuity. CIP is proud to have 19 key employees who have been with the company for 20+ years. Our core "family" of employees brings with them a sense of traditional commitment and dedication to your project that you won't find anywhere else, leading the way for our new employees with talent and fresh ideas to emulate.
Title: Department Head and Group Leader
               Company: EuroShop
Job Details
               EuroShop not only provides a forum for those on the supply and demand side to meet, it is also the world's most important retail forum for ideas and trends. This is why EuroShop 2011 will also have numerous special presentations in store. For instance, the EuroShop Designer Village allows visitors to gather targeted ideas from architect's offices and design studios for the design of tomorrow's stores and to find out about new trends. At the POPAI Village European and global POPAI (Point of Purchase Advertising International) member firms cover the complete cross-section of POP marketing. Renowned congresses and award ceremonies such as the EuroShop Retail Design Conference, the International EuroShop POP Conference and the Retail Technology Award underpin the standing of EuroShop as a leading global trade fair. Furthermore, trade visitors are invited to make use of free bilingual (German-English) forums for the complete duration of the trade fair such as the "EuroShop Forum Architektur & Design", the "POPAI Forum" and the "EuroCIS Forum". New at EuroShop 2011 is the "MQ" Area where prime display mannequin manufacturers are featured. In an architecturally appealing setting particularly high-quality mannequins will be on show for extraordinary product stagings.
